Package com.xebisco.yield

Klasse StandardPrefabs

java.lang.Object
com.xebisco.yield.StandardPrefabs
public class StandardPrefabs extends Object
The StandardPrefabs class provides methods for creating 2D entity prefabs with text, rectangles, and texture rectangles components.

    • text

      public static Entity2DPrefab text(String contents, Color color, Font font, String[] tags)
      This function creates a 2D entity prefab with text, color, font, and tags.
      Parameter:
      contents - The text contents that will be displayed by the Text component.
      color - The color parameter is a Color object that represents the color of the text. It can be used to set the color of the text to any desired color.
      font - The font parameter is of type Font and represents the font to be used for the text.
      tags - An array of strings that can be used to tag and identify the entity.
      Gibt zurück:
      An instance of the class Entity2DPrefab is being returned.

    • rectangleShape

      public static Entity2DPrefab rectangleShape(Class<? extends Rectangle> rectangleType, Vector2D size, Color color, Boolean filled, Double borderThickness, String[] tags)
      This function creates a rectangle entity with specified properties.
      Parameter:
      rectangleType - The class type of the rectangle component that will be created.
      size - The size of the rectangle, represented by a Size2D object.
      color - The color parameter is of type Color and represents the fill color of the rectangle.
      filled - A boolean value indicating whether the rectangle should be filled with color or not. If set to true, the rectangle will be filled with the specified color. If set to false, only the border of the rectangle will be drawn with the specified border color and thickness.
      borderThickness - borderThickness is a Double parameter that represents the thickness of the border of the rectangle. It is used in the creation of a new Entity2DPrefab object that contains a Rectangle component. If a value is provided for borderThickness, it will be set for the Rectangle component. If no value is
      tags - An array of strings that can be used to tag and identify the entity in the game engine.
      Gibt zurück:
      The method is returning an instance of the Entity2DPrefab class.

    • texRectangle

      public static Entity2DPrefab texRectangle(Vector2D size, String texturePath, String[] tags)
      This function creates a 2D entity prefab with a texture rectangle component of a specified size, texture path, and tags.
      Parameter:
      size - The size parameter is of type Size2D, which is a class representing a 2D size with width and height values. It is used to set the size of the TextureRectangle component in the Entity2DPrefab.
      texturePath - The texturePath parameter is a String that represents the file path or URL of the texture image that will be used for the TextureRectangle component.
      tags - An array of strings that can be used to tag and identify the entity.
      Gibt zurück:
      A `Entity2DPrefab` object is being returned.
